{"tid":745284,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2019DSE] 英文科／通識科交文區＋Reading Mock分享","createTime":"2018-07-16T15:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T10:26:12.000Z","uid":11058,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39bfd127476edd40bf9ccdf451fbf0435a0536d3","tid":745284,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T15:21:27.000Z","msg":"2019年度 *連登限定* 免費改文又開始啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n19DSE既同學仔係時候溫書啦作文操卷啦<br />\n今次送多份免費Mock比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交文好簡單<br />\n免費！<br />\n唯一代價係比我用你交既文教書！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n作完文／做完通識卷<br />\n可以send去awenglishls@gmail.com<br />\n我會盡快幫你改+比comments<br />\n7-14日內send翻比你 <br />\n不論past papers定係出版社題目都可以架 <br />\n<br />\n你可以<br />\n1. send .doc比我<br />\n2. send SCAN既手寫文比我 (可以用手機dl camscanner)<br />\n(影相就唔改啦好難睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有問題都可以係到問！！<br />\n<br />\nMock卷可以係下面download<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">非巴絲就去我IG去拎啦</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為左保障Mock卷唔會比有心人利用<br />\n做完之後麻煩大家IG Direct我拎答案啦~<br />\n<br />\n利申：小組補習導師 主修英文 英文通識5** <br />\nig: awenglishls"},{"pid":"ddadb567e550dbfcf270f0428158eead94004f46","tid":745284,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9986013ac18ce68d21c5145a6ae695303b6eb5db","tid":745284,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T01:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2972080730db6ebddb833cf63e848b5eae5358fb","tid":745284,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"Email: